    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Not so easy because if you do not update it after each keystroke, you will only update it \"after some time\" and it can lead also to weird behavior (the results are updated then suddenly the url is updated).\n\nThere's also a good chance that we are doing at each keystroke with the helper (cloning a lot of things) is slowing down it more.\n\nWe need a real perf investigation here before making choices.\n",
